Privacy Policy
We will not share or sell subscriber information with 3rd parties for their direct marketing purposes.
No mobile information will be shared with third parties/affiliates for marketing/promotional purposes.
All the above categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and consent; this information will not be shared with any third parties.
By selecting the Check Box on The Bookings Check Out Page Guests Agree to Receive Marketing SMS.
Guests may receive a SMS prior/during/after their stay with us.
Reply STOP to Opt Out. Standard message and data rates may apply.
